    <title>设计模式之工厂模式</title>
    <link href="http://sunjinhang.github.io/2020/02/05/FactoryPattern/"/>
    <id>http://sunjinhang.github.io/2020/02/05/FactoryPattern/</id>
    <published>2020-02-05T02:51:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-02-05T02:54:40.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1、创建图形接口"><a href="#1、创建图形接口" class="headerlink" title="1、创建图形接口"></a>1、创建图形接口</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public interface Shape &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">void draw();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、实现接口"><a href="#2、实现接口" class="headerlink" title="2、实现接口"></a>2、实现接口</h3><p>CircleImpl.java</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class CircleImpl implements Shape &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void <span class="function"><span class="title">draw</span></span>() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"this is circle method"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>SquareImpl.java</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class SquareImpl implements Shape &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void <span class="function"><span class="title">draw</span></span>() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"this is square method"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>RectangleImpl.java</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class RectangleImpl implements Shape &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Override</span><br><span class="line">public void <span class="function"><span class="title">draw</span></span>() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"this is rectangle method"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、创建图形工厂类"><a href="#3、创建图形工厂类" class="headerlink" title="3、创建图形工厂类"></a>3、创建图形工厂类</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class ShapeFactory &#123;</span><br><span class="line">public Shape getShape(String shape) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(shape == null) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> null;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(shape.equalsIgnoreCase(<span class="string">"circle"</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> new CircleImpl();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(shape.equalsIgnoreCase(<span class="string">"square"</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> new SquareImpl();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(shape.equalsIgnoreCase(<span class="string">"rectangle"</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> new RectangleImpl();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> null;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4、调用工厂类输出执行结果"><a href="#4、调用工厂类输出执行结果" class="headerlink" title="4、调用工厂类输出执行结果"></a>4、调用工厂类输出执行结果</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class FactoryPatternDemo &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">// TODO Auto-generated method stub</span><br><span class="line">ShapeFactory shapeFatory = new ShapeFactory();</span><br><span class="line">Shape circle = shapeFatory.getShape(<span class="string">"circle"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">circle.draw();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Shape square = shapeFatory.getShape(<span class="string">"square"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">square.draw();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Shape rectangle = shapeFatory.getShape(<span class="string">"rectangle"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">rectangle.draw();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行结果 ：</p>]]></content>
    
